-- DabbaMap — 144 claimable stub listings with pre-computed coordinates
-- Paste this entire block into the Supabase SQL editor and click Run.
-- stub=true  →  "Claim this listing" button is visible on each card.
-- is_claimed=false  →  listing is open for anyone to claim.
-- lat/lng are baked in — no geocoding needed. Positions are within ~3 km of each area centre.

